  "action_required": true,

  "body": "Companion to the 10:00 memo. Codifies the missing-from-prior principle (openbraid is HOSTING layer; orgdef.openthing artifacts are CONTENT layer — openbraid ingests them as source of truth, does not invent its own data model) AND scopes Phase E concretely: E1 orgdef ingestion (upload path; fetch-from-git deferred to F), E2 job artifact ingestion, E3 roledef resolution (on-demand), E4 URL space exposure (per prior memo's three-level semantics), E5 full-fidelity export. Out of scope: mirror sync mechanics, PUBLIC/PROTECTED auth, memo URLs, URL versioning, canonical-template handling. Success criteria: Thingalog round-trip dogfood + cross-runtime instantiation + five spec-org ingest. Complaint-shaped experience memo back on ship. Full content in companion .body.md file.",
  "body_ref": "2026-05-10-1030--orgdef-strategist--openbraid-strategist--phase-e-orgdef-ingestion-and-url-space.body.md",

